node.text:
The freshly remastered version of the Speedster project has been finally launched in the new Carbon Sea-Dweller series. A long-awaited project for those who prefer a larger watch in the wrist, as it comes in a 43mm case. Could you be one of the lucky 10?⁣
⁣
⁣
⁣
⁣
#DiW #seadweller43 #carbonSC #seadweller43mm #seadweller#designaindividualwatches #bespokewatch #watchcollector #watchessentials #watchoftheday #custommade #rolexwrist #rolexwatch #customrolex #customwatch
